{"tid":1590560,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[圍爐]一人n個不應該氣餒嘅原因","createTime":"2019-09-23T18:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T14:00:09.000Z","uid":45519,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"48ce7b04fe7e9850af6a4a5c3e34161c56fc4d60","tid":1590560,"uid":45519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:57:43.000Z","msg":"見過手足俾人打、見過前線俾狗拉而救唔到，係咪好內疚，喊到仆街？<br />\n<br />\n而返到屋企，一切好似冇進展，<br />\n只係承受咗更多嘅痛苦，<br />\n見到有人快樂抗爭，甚至如常生活，<br />\n又嬲又氣餒？<br />\n<br />\n其實我都係。<br />\n<br />\n但我永遠都會記得，<br />\n有一日放工去咗人鏈，<br />\n散緊果陣，<br />\n有個嬸嬸踩住單車岩岩到。<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 單車嬸嬸：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嬸嬸：你地散架啦？乜冇差佬咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：唔見呀，應該冇事，我地都解散啦，antie你趕過黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嬸嬸：冇呀，放工聽到你地有聲，咪黎望下，幫你地睇下有冇啲衰警察。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：冇事呀，走架啦我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嬸嬸：好啦，咁我都返屋企，仲諗住有得黎幫手睇差佬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後嬸嬸拖著單車同我一齊行，<br />\n一路行一路有人嗌口號，當中有人嗌香復香港。<br />\n突然間佢俾我地任何人都大聲疾呼，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嬸嬸：時代革命！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果一刻，我眼眶打轉，<br />\n世界好殘酷，我們很可愛，<br />\n佢想用佢嘅方法保護我地，<br />\n我地想用我地嘅方法保護佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為咗阻止惡毒卑劣嘅人，<br />\n伸手去打爛我地依個家園，<br />\n我會願意承受一切，<br />\n讓保存佢地嘅單純和可愛。"},{"pid":"15e4eb59596f12c6743d857019bcb863287367c5","tid":1590560,"uid":45519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:58:06.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺"},{"pid":"47ca1696cf266d1d63486d3b796faf254977486b","tid":1590560,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"47ba71240b32932e2df8ddd78945ca5be77d8f82","tid":1590560,"uid":45519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:58:19.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"7a8d4339f72e92f26bdcba7d2b007da179671f46","tid":1590560,"uid":45519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:58:40.000Z","msg":"All in or nothing"},{"pid":"c90f60c9a9da7886b92163c4f46ee80d6ea758d7","tid":1590560,"uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:58:45.000Z","msg":"我只得堅持。。。我喜歡堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b838d550a9a8630a0067e41b26a6ea2faa451a","tid":1590560,"uid":45519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:59:47.000Z","msg":"因為想最後可以一齊返屋企。"},{"pid":"1653e793088cd495ac09c97733585e8a09f538c1","tid":1590560,"uid":45519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:00:25.000Z","msg":"唔准氣餒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb4ba976b6d9335c8e0394b5ac8547d4183f7fc","tid":1590560,"uid":45519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />給所有手足一個擁抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0095486e5b8e7f2d9243d446885